{"tid":769611,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[紅磚大學] PIE LEE HDISE AOS PEM ISE LEM EEM 新生資訊及相認區","createTime":"2018-08-06T10:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T11:45:23.000Z","uid":158150,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"92492fcbf1cd7ac10a0d5e55f6a4829bcaf754b4","tid":769611,"uid":158150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T10:19:33.000Z","msg":"大家好呀 唔知有無Ching今年Jupas或者Non Jupas都係入PIE LEE HDISE AOS PEM ISE LEM EEM呢8科呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTelegram：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/ERcR_k8cRvljzlK10NUbGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FERcR_k8cRvljzlK10NUbGQ&d=ZLJBKvFJn1mqTae%2FYKNFg8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=33712076\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/ERcR_k8cRvljzlK10NUbGQ</a><br />\n<br />\n裡面有讀呢八科既師兄姐可以解答你地既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無論係Ocamp, reg day, reg 科,前途之類既野都可以問我地嫁人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddde07f6d2740117a206fe74308759fe937ac069","tid":769611,"uid":158150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T10:23:28.000Z","msg":"咁經Jupas入讀ISE部門就有三科<br />\n分別係<br />\n物流及企業工程（榮譽）理學士學位組合課程 JS3571 (LEE)<br />\n產品及工業工程（榮譽）工學士學位組合課程JS3557 (PIE)<br />\n工業及系統工程高級文憑 JS3117<br />\n(HDISE)<br />\n頭兩科就year 2要揀科讀 好似 LEE 就揀物流或企業管理（LEM/EEM）<br />\nPIE 就要揀產品設計或工業系統（PEM/ISE）<br />\n呢幾科出路都幾廣 好多工都可以返 而且產品系統 物流都有工程師牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262117590f870c47b1a74e7b24dca35eb36573ea","tid":769611,"uid":158150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T10:24:32.000Z","msg":"同大家介紹返一d關於ISE department同oday既資訊先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[PIE] (JS3557) Bachelor of Engineering (Honours) Scheme in Product and Industrial Engineering<br />\n產品及工業工程(榮譽)工學士學位組合課程<br />\n<br />\n[LEE] (JS3571) Bachelor of Science (Honours) Scheme in Logistics and Enterprise Engineering<br />\n物流及企業工程(榮譽)理學士學位組合課程<br />\n<br />\n[HDISE] (JS3117) Higher Diploma in Industrial and Systems Engineering 工業及系統工程學高級文憑<br />\n<br />\n以下為經NON-JUPAS入ISE Department既5科<br />\n<br />\n[AOS] Bachelor of Science (Honours) in Aviation Operations and Systems<br />\n航空營運及系統學(榮譽)理學士學位<br />\n<br />\n[PEM] Bachelor of Engineering (Honours) in Product Engineering with Marketing<br />\n產品工程兼市場學(榮譽)工學士學位<br />\n<br />\n[ISE] Bachelor of Engineering (Honours) in Industrial and Systems Engineering<br />\n工業及系統工程學(榮譽)工學士學位<br />\n<br />\n[LEM] Bachelor of Science (Honours) in Logistics Engineering with Management <br />\n物流工程兼管理(榮譽)理學士學位<br />\n<br />\n[EEM] Bachelor of Science (Honours) in Enterprise Engineering with Management<br />\n企業工程兼管理(榮譽)理學士學位<br />\n<br />\n[Registration] <br />\n當你係JUPAS收到Offer之後, 記得要係8月7號17:00之前, 交返$5000 JUPAS留位費, 先叫做正式Accept左Offer。之後就要係(8月9-10號)係online搞埋Registration程序，直到報ocamp先要返poly。<br />\n<br />\n[Orientation Day] <br />\n今年既Orientation Day (下稱Oday)會係8月12-13日舉行，地點係邵逸夫體育館（VA樓地下）（下稱Shaw）。 主要係俾Freshmen註冊學生會會員同埋報O Camp<br />\n<br />\n當日大家要準備既野包括: <br />\n1. 現金（報ocamp之用）(1個ocamp約$250-500)<br />\n2. 身份證 <br />\n3. eAdmission 既Notice of offer <br />\n4. SU Fee比咗錢嘅Finance Office網上收據(顯示比咗錢) 或者 自己SU Fee debit note hard copy+唔同比錢方法收據(入數紙又或者網上過數等)<br />\n5. 迎新營活動家長/監護人同意書<br />\n (未滿十八歲嘅freshman要填完交去booth）<br />\n<br />\n最後最後，再次歡迎咁多位同學仔加入ISE依個大家庭<br />\n <br />\n有咩問題歡迎係到問或者入telegram group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26cc3e12878ed19c82690a79ecc7b381760a4ae5","tid":769611,"uid":194137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T10:35:16.000Z","msg":"我係今年pie 新生 想問下多唔多女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b520ef54bbadd50da5f596615103fde3102079b7","tid":769611,"uid":158150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T10:37:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係今年pie 新生 想問下多唔多女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以我所知 pie有呢個男女既黃金比例 相信都多女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋眾所週知 ise係feng裡面最多女既department<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3116496ab2266e55d09a27dad10303923c85b3b6","tid":769611,"uid":198551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T10:49:37.000Z","msg":"我想問下可以報咩類型嘅o camp？求巴打絲下解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8509e55902b84c5c79cbc14ae5ead1bea7d7e0bf","tid":769611,"uid":53948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b520ef54bbadd50da5f596615103fde3102079b7","tid":769611,"uid":158150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T10:37:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係今年pie 新生 想問下多唔多女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class